OL,7,FEmergency care at Basingstoke and
OL,8,FNorth Hampshire Hospital has been
OL,9,Frated as ''requires improvement''.
OL,11,FIt comes after an inspection last
OL,12,Fsummer by the Care Quality Commission
OL,13,Ffound failings hadn't all been
OL,14,Fresolved since their last visit in
OL,15,F2020.
OL,17,FThey re-rated the A&E department as
OL,18,Fneeding improvement. The care provided
OL,19,Ffor mental health patients was of
OL,20,Fparticular concern.
