OL,7,FHampshire Hospitals NHS Trust accepts
OL,8,Fthe findings and says it's working
OL,9,Fhard on improvements. The overall
OL,10,Frating for the hospital and the Trust
OL,11,Fremain ''good''.
OL,13,FInspectors found some patients,
OL,14,Fparticularly those with mental health
OL,15,Fconditions, weren't always receiving
OL,16,Fcare in a safe environment.
OL,18,FThe report also found staff hadn't
OL,19,Falways completed critical mandatory
OL,20,Ftraining, and there were gaps in
OL,21,Fobservation records.
