OL,5,Cimprovement'
OL,7,FChief nurse Julie Dawes said the
OL,8,Freport was disappointing, but they
OL,9,Faccepted the findings.
OL,11,FShe said: "First of all, I'd like to
OL,12,Fapologise to patients. So patients,
OL,13,Fyou know, have not been receiving the
OL,14,Fcare that we aspire to. I'm sorry to
OL,15,Fthose.
OL,17,F"We are really dedicated to make these
OL,18,Fimprovements, and our teams are
OL,19,Fworking really really hard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
