OL,7,F"And I'm pleased to say that actually
OL,8,Feven since the visit in July, we have
OL,9,Falready addressed many of the issues
OL,10,Fthat were raised with us.
OL,12,F"And in fact, a few weeks ago, the CQC
OL,13,Fcame out round on an informal visit,
OL,14,Fand we were able to share and show
OL,15,Fthem many of the improvements we've
OL,16,Fmade."
