OL,7,FAfter the last inspection 5 years ago
OL,8,Fa safe room was put in place for
OL,9,Fpatients with mental health issues but
OL,10,Fduring Covid the department was
OL,11,Freconfigured.
OL,13,FNow three safe rooms are being put in
OL,14,F- one for children is already in use
OL,15,Fand an adult room is nearing
OL,16,Fcompletion.
OL,18,FInspectors also noted many examples of
OL,19,Fkind and compassionate care from staff
OL,20,Fin the emergency department.
