OL,5,Cimprovement'
OL,7,FAnd they said the service had
OL,8,Fintroduced earlier assessments by
OL,9,Fsenior doctors, cutting waiting times
OL,10,Fand supporting the low tolerance of
OL,11,Ftreating patients in corridors.
OL,13,FThe CQC recognised that the trust has
OL,14,Fmade some improvements but said it
OL,15,Fwill continue to monitor the service
OL,16,Fto make sure people consistently
OL,17,Freceive safe and effective care.
